article.description: — Will Pruitt scored 27 points as Lipscomb beat Bellarmine 90-74 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Pruitt's 27 lead Lipscomb over Bellarmine 90-74
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Will Pruitt scored 27 points as Lipscomb beat Bellarmine 90-74 on Wednesday night. Pruitt also contributed seven rebounds and six assists for the Bisons (19-11, 10-5 Atlantic Sun Conference). A.J McGinnis scored 18 points, shooting 5 for 11 (3 for 6 from 3-point range) and 5 of 6 from the free throw line. Joe Anderson was 5 of 8 shooting (2 for 3 from 3-point range) to finish with 12 points. Bash Wieland led the Knights (8-22, 4-11) in scoring, finishing with 18 points, eight rebounds and four assists. Ben Johnson added 17 points for Bellarmine. In addition, Langdon Hatton had 16 points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
